quantities (\ref{transpol})-(\ref{poldistr}). But for a
construction of various nucleon EM structure models the
flavour-independent iso-scalar and iso-vector parts $F^N_{1s}(t),
F^N_{1v}(t), F^N_{2s}(t), F^N_{2v}(t)$ of the Dirac and Pauli FFs
to be defined by a parametrization of the matrix element of the
nucleon EM current

